{"tid":1369583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"727元朗自由行攻略","createTime":"2019-07-26T17:35:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T06:29:19.000Z","uid":237133,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"bfd4e05af1dc887d2c93a95d421a463392c89cd6","tid":1369583,"uid":237133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:35:59.000Z","msg":"雖然政府已經發出反對通知書，但如果大家仍然想去元朗一遊，建議參考以下那年十七巴打介紹元朗嘅資料:<br />\n<br />\n圍村土生土長，想同大家分析圍村生態同地勢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1361067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1361067</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n然後再睇下J.Spearing巴打好有心機整嘅元朗勢力分佈圖:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PL88ied.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPL88ied.png&h=c734f0b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就可以知道，元朗就係鄉村包圍城市，兼且算係香港一個比較複雜嘅地區，而居民普遍對我地會冇咁友善，我地嘅目的唔係要樹敵，而係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">connect！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以我地要堅持三大原則：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不入村</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不破壞</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不放火</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">727絕對係和理非主場！勇武今次行埋一邊先！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n跟住就會逐步講要注意嘅地方。"},{"pid":"d8546e3a4c9c4815caff55e9649996a88bf6af92","tid":1369583,"uid":237133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:57:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">裝備篇：</span><br />\n<br />\n話明自由行，當然同平時遊行有d唔同啦！<br />\n<br />\n基本裝束：<br />\n1. 替換嘅衣物(保持衞生)<br />\n2. 大量清水(當然係解渴)<br />\n3. 雨遮(當然係遮太陽同擋雨)，長柄好過縮骨(大把d，可以遮到大d範圍)<br />\n4. 雨褸(小朋友適用，大人亦無不可)<br />\n5. 乾糧(因為未必有補給站)<br />\n<br />\n今次係和理非自由行，但個別巴打需要多少少防禦裝備亦無不可，而呢班巴打需要喺自由行路程嘅<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">前、中、後</span>都要出現，詳情之後再講。"},{"pid":"71122179de607e0e35c10fc22aad8234e95e214b","tid":1369583,"uid":237133,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:15:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">元朗居民篇：</span><br />\n<br />\n首先，喺元朗圍村居住嘅巴絲，我唔贊成今次出嚟啦。第一，你地出咗去，萬一比人點相，或者你同家人都會有麻煩；第二，其實留番喺村，可以<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">通風報信</span></span>，一樣幫到自由行<br />\n<br />\n元朗市中心嘅巴絲，如果可以，不妨先出門睇下各主要路口，睇下有無異動，然後去到外區人都到嘅時候，先join自由行，走嗰陣最好換到衫，甚至可以跟大隊去屯門天水圍，甚至市區，食個飯睇場戲行個大運先返屋企<br />\n<br />\n原則：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不可落單</span></span><br />\n<br />\n跟住講外區人點入嚟。"},{"pid":"9d53d2c30cd20641df72c442ee4253e2a57f2da7","tid":1369583,"uid":237133,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T19:33:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">外區居民篇：</span><br />\n<br />\n之前申請遊行起點係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">水邊村遊樂場</span></span>，其實係一個好小嘅球場，好快會企滿，唔知使唔使要用埋隔離嘅元朗大球場啦<br />\n<br />\n屯門天水圍嘅巴絲，估計多數搭輕鐵嚟，喺<span style=\"color: green;\">水邊圍站</span>或者<span style=\"color: green;\">豐年路站</span>落車就得<br />\n<br />\n市區同荃灣巴絲，多數最快係搭西鐵，應該喺<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">朗屏站</span></span>落車<br />\n<br />\n然後可以咁行：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vZRYFTJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvZRYFTJ.jpg&h=a33283f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">朗屏站B2出口</span></span>上行人天橋，經過<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">元朗廣場</span></span>(地圖上無標示，但去到好難miss)同行人天橋再過馬路就到<br />\n<br />\n巴士路線方面，附近有3個巴士站：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">元朗西巴士總站</span></span>: <br />\n<br />\n嚟自以下地區巴絲可以坐到尾：<br />\n<br />\n54<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">上村</span></span><br />\n<br />\n64K <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">大埔</span></span><br />\n<br />\n68M <span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">荃灣</span></span><br />\n<br />\n968 <span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港島</span></span><br />\n<br />\n跟住去隔離元朗廣場2/F上行人天橋就會去到<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">元朗警署巴士站</span></span><br />\n<br />\n嗰度停靠路線如下：<br />\n<br />\n68X<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大角咀，深水埗，長沙灣</span></span><br />\n<br />\n268B<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">紅磡，尖沙咀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n268C <span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">觀塘，黃大仙</span></span><br />\n<br />\n268X<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佐敦，旺角</span></span><br />\n<br />\n269D<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">沙田</span></span><br />\n<br />\n行前少少過咗馬路就係球場<br />\n<br />\n仲有一個球場前面嘅站就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">水邊村</span></span><br />\n<br />\n276同276P來自<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">上水</span></span><br />\n<br />\n為免受可能嘅封路影響，請早少少出發，汀九橋同博愛迴旋處有機會比較塞"},{"pid":"e9cd906733e5fa3f7a2561ed5d14a8ad9ac84a42","tid":1369583,"uid":52282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T20:11:37.000Z","msg":"師兄知唔知確認咗既集合時間係幾點？"},{"pid":"73c8c689f7083c4a58e109cbbe6229f00bf1dcd6","tid":1369583,"uid":237133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T20:16:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">路線篇：</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JFVyu8M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJFVyu8M.png&h=c7fdb76a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前有巴打提交過呢條路線，但如今無遊行，路線純粹供參考<br />\n<br />\n如果一直沿大馬路行去元朗站，正常半小時已經行完，不過屆時可能會好多人，亦都唔知警方封路情形係點<br />\n<br />\n大馬路中間有輕鐵路軌，警方有機會只係封西行或者東行線，行軍速度可能會好慢<br />\n<br />\n同喺港島情況唔同，元朗小商舖相對對我地無咁友善，未必會大開中門，個别甚至會暫停營業<br />\n<br />\n想食嘢，補給，最佳地點就一定係近起點嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">元朗廣場</span></span>，估計會有食肆同超市(Taste)營業，部份連登仔嘅comfort food吉野家在此<br />\n<br />\n洗手間最好喺元廣去埋<br />\n<br />\n其他沿路嘅喜利，開心廣場情況相對不明<br />\n<br />\n大馬路開心廣場前小小近大棠路站有麥記<br />\n<br />\n有小型食肆老闆同伙計會唔歡迎我地呢d&ldquo;黃屍暴徒&quot;，記住唔使嗌交，connect到就最好，唔得就算<br />\n<br />\n恆香行過咗大棠路就會見到<br />\n<br />\n唔鼓勵大家太偏離大馬路，想試勝利牛丸，好到底，佳記小食等等，下次先<br />\n<br />\n可以勇武小小嘅巴打，除咗<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">前、中、後</span></span>都要有之外，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">側邊</span>都應該要有，同平時喺市區行好唔同，絲打老人家小朋友行中間，兩邊巴打保護！<br />\n<br />\n如果4:00之後先到元朗，要觀察係咪已經喺龍尾，成個自由行最好6:00前完成，如果join唔到反而應該走去朗屏或者元朗兩個西鐵站幫手"},{"pid":"b18a8199b6444592cf7b742377f8b573fa7cb91f","tid":1369583,"uid":237133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9cd906733e5fa3f7a2561ed5d14a8ad9ac84a42","tid":1369583,"uid":52282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T20:11:37.000Z","msg":"師兄知唔知確認咗既集合時間係幾點？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T20:17:11.000Z","msg":"冇人知<br />\n<br />\nassume 最遲3:00<br />\n<br />\n6:00前完成"},{"pid":"662a3c0d671afec6fe709bbed849339d1597acbe","tid":1369583,"uid":52282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b18a8199b6444592cf7b742377f8b573fa7cb91f","tid":1369583,"uid":237133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9cd906733e5fa3f7a2561ed5d14a8ad9ac84a42","tid":1369583,"uid":52282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T20:11:37.000Z","msg":"師兄知唔知確認咗既集合時間係幾點？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T20:17:11.000Z","msg":"冇人知<br />\n<br />\nassume 最遲3:00<br />\n<br />\n6:00前完成"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T20:18:28.000Z","msg":"唔該晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽日見"},{"pid":"6e613d59a89c4cfd83222a5d7a07f5f6b8fb0e3e","tid":1369583,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T20:21:29.000Z","msg":"12:00-18:00<br />\n全部齊裝 好有可能白衫潛水變警民衝突！"},{"pid":"515c04e0e420aec722530a2ce32421aca0ec8ad8","tid":1369583,"uid":237133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T20:35:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">回家篇：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<br />\n元朗站好近南邊圍同十八鄉鄉事委員會，和理非勇武都要打醒十二分精神！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n真係想去Yoho I Yoho II或者想留元朗記住要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>換衫</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但唔鼓勵留</span></span><br />\n<br />\n元朗市巴絲最好<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">跟大隊走先</span></span>或者去Yoho I 或II hea下<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>大原則：不可落單！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">其他無去元朗嘅巴絲，特別住新界嘅，要留意該區情況，黃昏時可以到港鐵站或者主要巴士站觀察，必要時護送自由行過嘅巴絲老幼返屋企</span></span>"},{"pid":"56251c2da1a718263d459c9e630d35fb7a182382","tid":1369583,"uid":237133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T20:40:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">逃生篇：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">萬一有事要識避識走！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">可以參考：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香城Online 元朗副本完全逃生手冊（修訂版）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1368760\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1368760</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">祝大家開心自由行，安全回家！一個都不能少！</span>"},{"pid":"42673b36bda72d192883e6953cc45d02950ba3ec","tid":1369583,"uid":237133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T20:41:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d1efd6cf91c570b42fbc584902c9cb147757597c","tid":1369583,"uid":280338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T20:42:31.000Z","msg":"Push 我要聽朝個個都見到"},{"pid":"5fd3c2140e17a1b41d844a29b58894